summary: This Mod Makes Apples, Chicken Breast, Cabbage, and all other foodstuffs no longer Grant 2-5hp Per Piece. Makes food much more potent in Magnitude than before.
descriptionHtml:
This Mod Makes Apples, Chicken Breast, Cabbage, and all other foodstuffs no longer Grant 2-5hp Per Piece. Makes food much more potent in Magnitude than before.

-Chicken Breast Cooked (Restore 30HP)
-Cabbage (Restore 25HP)
-Apples (Restore 25HP)
-Cooked Salmon (Restore 20HP)
-Bread (Restore 25HP)
-Carrots (Restore 10HP)
-Tomatoes (Restore 15HP)

This mod also stacks potency with ALL other Cooking Overhaul Mods, It Rewrites Original Potency of Food so it Stacks Appropriately With all other Cooking Modules. Such As,

Wolferoo's (Wolfs) Cooking Recipes
Grommit's Cooking Overhaul
Cooking Expanded
Babette's Feast.

So Get it now and Enjoy More Potent Better Food, because Restoring 5hp Per Cabbage Eaten was just Rediculous.
author: sw33tsp0t
